21
00:01:41,730 --> 00:01:43,900
我跟他说：别跟我说这个
I told him, "get away from me with that."

22
00:01:43,900 --> 00:01:46,630
他一边走一边说你是专门制造麻烦的人
He walked away from me calling you a troublemaker.

23
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:48,630
伦德先生怎样说？
What Mr. Rand say?

24
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:50,470
