That's what one of them white fellas tell me.

30
00:01:58,810 --> 00:02:00,150
我才不担心他们会辞退我
I ain't worried about them firing me.

31
00:02:00,150 --> 00:02:02,620
就因为我问了个问题，他们就要辞退我？
What, they gonna fire me 'cause I asked a question?

32
00:02:02,620 --> 00:02:03,720
我只问了个问题
That's all I did.

33
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:05,790
还说：什么西瓜，伦德先生？
I went to Mr. Rand and I asked him.

34
00:02:05,860 --> 00:02:07,060
我问他：为何？
I asked him, "why?

35
00:02:07,090 --> 00:02:09,190
为何你让所有白人负责驾驶，而有色人种就去搬运？
Why you got all the white mens driving, and the colored lifting?"

36
00:02:09,190 --> 00:02:11,190
跟他说：什么事了？我不重要吗？
Told him, "what's the matter? Don't I count?

37
00:02:11,190 --> 00:02:13,460
你以为只有白人才够聪明去驾驶吗？
Think only white fellows got sense enough to drive a truck?"

38
00:02:13,460 --> 00:02:15,660
