just tell the truth.

45
00:02:29,580 --> 00:02:31,480
这只不过是因为你投诉了
Ain't nothing but somebody trumped it up on you

46
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:32,610
所以有人要诬蔑你
'cause you filed a complaint on.

47
00:02:32,610 --> 00:02:33,850
布朗尼没那么聪明
Brownie ain't got that much sense.

48
00:02:33,850 --> 00:02:35,180
他什么事也不去想
Man wasn't thinking about nothing.

49
00:02:35,180 --> 00:02:36,950
我只想他们改正职位描述
All I want them to do is change the job description,

50
00:02:36,950 --> 00:02:39,520
给所有人一个机会去驾驶，开车
give everybody a chance to drive the truck. Oi!

51
00:02:39,650 --> 00:02:43,590
布朗尼没想过这，他不是很聪明
Brownie can't see that. He ain't got that much sense.

52
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:05,910
你怎么知道他一直在跟
How you figure he be making out

53
00:03:05,910 --> 00:03:08,580
泰勒的酒吧里那个女子调情？
with that gal, be up in Taylors' all the time?

54
00:03:08,580 --> 00:03:10,250
- 那个叫艾伯塔的女子  - 谁？
- That Alberta gal?  - Who?

55
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:11,220
布朗尼
Brownie.

56
00:03:11,250 --> 00:03:14,020
我跟他经常在一起，就像我们一样
Same as you and me, getting about as much as we is.

57
00:03:14,020 --> 00:03:16,760
- 心照不宣吧  - 是吗？
- Which is to say nothing.  - It is, huh?

58
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:19,490
我想你比我更猜得透他吧
Well, I figure you doing a little better than me.

59
00:03:19,490 --> 00:03:20,890
我不会跟你说我在猜什么
And I ain't saying what I'm doing!

60
00:03:20,900 --> 00:03:22,860
朋友，听着，我太了解你
Nigger, look here. I know you.

61
00:03:22,860 --> 00:03:24,900
难怕你只接近了她一点
If you had gotten anywhere near that gal,

62
00:03:24,900 --> 00:03:27,270
