as long as I keep up my vigilance,

347
00:13:17,420 --> 00:13:19,120
他就得打上一场硬仗
he gonna have to fight to get me.

348
00:13:19,130 --> 00:13:20,360
我不会轻易让他带走我
I ain't going easy.

349
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:24,400
