No, Rose, thanks. I just was in the neighborhood

377
00:14:18,220 --> 00:14:19,550
想着进来看你们一下
and thought I'd stop by for a minute.

378
00:14:19,550 --> 00:14:21,220
得了吧，你刚巧经过这
Yeah, you was in the neighborhood all right.

379
00:14:21,290 --> 00:14:22,190
老兄，你还真会说话
Nigger, you telling the truth there.

380
