You was in the neighborhood 'cause it's my payday.

381
00:14:24,360 --> 00:14:26,660
既然你提到了，给我十块
Well, hell, since you mentioned it, let me have $10.

382
00:14:26,660 --> 00:14:30,500
该死的，我宁愿下地狱
I'll be damned. I'll die and go to hell

383
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:33,230
和魔鬼玩牌也不会给你
and play Blackjack with the devil before I give you $10.

384
00:14:33,230 --> 00:14:36,200
我想知道你看见过的魔鬼
That's what I want to know about, that devil you done seen.

385
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:38,370
爸看见过魔鬼？真会吹牛
Pop done seen the devil? You too much, pop.

386
00:14:38,370 --> 00:14:40,540
- 对，我见过  - 他才没有
