00:15:00,030 --> 00:15:00,930
那怎办？
What to do?

395
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:02,960
我只有些破烂的家具
I got an empty house with some raggedy furniture.

396
00:15:03,030 --> 00:15:03,930
科丽没有床
Cory ain't got no bed.

397
