他在地上铺点破布就睡了
He's sleeping on a pile of rags on the floor.

398
00:15:06,400 --> 00:15:08,500
每天都工作，却不能贷款
Working every day, can't get no credit.

399
00:15:08,500 --> 00:15:09,970
