Come a knock on the door.

402
00:15:13,270 --> 00:15:15,540
我才住在这里三天，有谁知道我在这？
I ain't been living but three days, who know I'm here?

403
00:15:15,540 --> 00:15:17,680
我去应门，原来是魔鬼
