Now, I told him, he give me them three rooms,

413
00:15:35,260 --> 00:15:36,600
多少都行
he can charge whatever he want.

414
00:15:36,600 --> 00:15:38,430
有辆货车第二天来了
Next day, a truck pull up here,

415
00:15:38,430 --> 00:15:40,230
两个男人给那三间房间布置了家具
two men unload them three rooms.

416
00:15:40,230 --> 00:15:42,430
驾车的那位给了我本书
Man what drove the truck give me a book.

417
00:15:42,440 --> 00:15:45,970
跟我说每月初，寄十块到书上这个地址
Said first of the month, send $10 to the address in the book,

418
00:15:45,970 --> 00:15:47,240
那就可以了
everything'll be fine.

419
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:48,270
说如果你没付
Said if you miss a payment,

420
00:15:48,270 --> 00:15:51,440
魔鬼会来找你，而你需要付上更多
the devil was coming back, and there'll be hell to pay.

421
00:15:51,450 --> 00:15:53,010
那是十五年前的事
That was 15 years ago.

422
00:15:53,010 --> 00:15:56,620
直至今天，每月初，我都寄十块
To this day, first day of every month, I send my $10,

423
00:15:56,620 --> 00:15:58,280
