just like clockwork. Rose'll tell you.

424
00:15:58,290 --> 00:15:59,520
特洛伊在说谎
Troy lying.

425
00:15:59,520 --> 00:16:01,250
我从此没再见过那人
I ain't never seen that man since.

426
00:16:01,350 --> 00:16:02,990
你说如果他不是魔鬼会是谁？
Now, you tell me, who else that gonna be but the devil?

427
00:16:02,990 --> 00:16:05,320
而我没有卖掉灵魂什么的
And I ain't sold my soul or nothing like that.

428
00:16:05,330 --> 00:16:07,790
我不会跟坐着货车来的魔鬼交易
No, I wouldn't have, truck with the devil over nothing like that.

429
00:16:07,790 --> 00:16:11,600
但我却换来所有家具，所以我准时寄我的十块
