钱该花在露西尔的冰箱上而不是放在梅隆银行内
Mellon don't need that money as bad as Lucille wants that refrigerator.

1640
01:11:55,710 --> 01:11:56,780
我很清楚
I know that.

1641
01:11:56,780 --> 01:11:57,810
- 告诉你吧  - 什么？
- Tell you what I'll do.  - What?

1642
01:11:57,810 --> 01:11:59,980
当你为罗斯建成籓篱时
When you finish building this fence for Rose,

1643
01:11:59,980 --> 01:12:01,810
我就给露西尔买冰箱
I'll buy Lucille that refrigerator.

1644
01:12:01,810 --> 01:12:04,750
你会后悔的
You done stuck your foot in your mouth now.

1645
01:12:05,820 --> 01:12:07,380
朋友，你要去哪？
Hey, nigger, where you going?

1646
01:12:07,380 --> 01:12:08,820
我得回家
I'm going home.

1647
01:12:08,820 --> 01:12:10,720
你不是在想我会帮你吧
I know you don't expect me to help you now.

1648
01:12:10,720 --> 01:12:12,090
我得保住我的钱
I'm protecting my money.

1649
01:12:12,690 --> 01:12:15,690
我想看你一个人慢慢的建
I want to see you put that fence up by yourself.

1650
01:12:15,690 --> 01:12:17,130
那就是我想看的
That's what I want to see.

1651
01:12:17,130 --> 01:12:19,690
没有我的帮忙，六个月后你仍然毫无头绪
You'll be here another six months without me.

1652
01:12:19,700 --> 01:12:20,960
朋友，那样不对啊
Nigger, you ain't right.

1653
01:12:20,960 --> 01:12:22,830
当谈到我的钱
When it come to my money,

1654
01:12:22,830 --> 01:12:25,930
我就像国庆日的烟火一样对[好]
I'm right as fireworks on the Fourth of July.

1655
01:12:25,940 --> 01:12:27,400
等着瞧
We gonna see.

1656
01:12:27,400 --> 01:12:29,100
你准备去提款吧！
You better get out your bank book!

1657
01:13:21,020 --> 01:13:23,160
他们在警局在说了什么？加布怎了？
What they say down there? What's happening with Gabe?

1658
01:13:23,160 --> 01:13:26,190
我过去接回他了，花了我五十块
I went down there and got him out. Cost me $50.

1659
01:13:26,200 --> 01:13:27,900
说他在扰乱秩序
Said he was disturbing the peace.

1660
01:13:27,900 --> 01:13:30,200
法官三周后审讯
Judge set up a hearing for him in three weeks

1661
01:13:30,200 --> 01:13:33,000
他为何不被重新分配到医院内
to show cause why he shouldn't be recommitted.

1662
01:13:33,000 --> 01:13:34,870
那你怎说？你怎跟法官说的
What'd you say? What'd you tell the judge?

1663
01:13:35,040 --> 01:13:36,910
我跟他说我会照顾他
I told him I'd take care of him.

1664
01:13:36,910 --> 01:13:38,470
没有理由又分配他住医院
It didn't make no sense to recommit the man.

1665
01:13:38,480 --> 01:13:39,970
他伸出他那贪婪的手
He stuck out his big greasy palm,

1666
01:13:39,980 --> 01:13:42,780
跟我说交出五十块然后带他回家
told me to give him $50 and take him on home.

1667
01:13:42,780 --> 01:13:44,780
那他现在在哪？
Where's he at now? Where'd he go off to?

1668
01:13:44,780 --> 01:13:46,780
又到处乱跑了，他不想别人拖着他的手
Gone about his business. He don't need nobody to hold his hand.

1669
01:13:46,780 --> 01:13:49,020
我也不知道，但那看来是最好的选择
Well, I don't know, seem like that would be the best place for him.

1670
01:13:49,020 --> 01:13:50,050
让他住在医院里
To put him in a hospital.

1671
01:13:50,050 --> 01:13:51,190
我知道你接下来要说什么
I know what you say gonna say,

1672
01:13:51,190 --> 01:13:52,820
但那正是我认为这样做是对的原因
but that's what I think would be best.

1673
01:13:52,820 --> 01:13:54,460
那他在打仗时失去的一切，为了什么？
Man had his life ruined fighting for what?

1674
01:13:54,460 --> 01:13:55,890
现在他们想把他锁起来？
Now, they want to take him and lock him up?

1675
01:13:55,890 --> 01:13:58,190
该给他自由啊，他又没打扰谁
Let him be free. Man ain't bothering nobody.

1676
01:13:58,200 --> 01:14:02,060
我想每个人都有不同的看法
Everybody got their own way of looking at it, I guess.

1677
01:14:02,070 --> 01:14:03,470
来拿你的午餐吧
Come on, get your lunch.

1678
01:14:03,470 --> 01:14:05,100
我这里有些棉豆和玉米面包
I got some lima beans and cornbread in the oven.

1679
01:14:05,170 --> 01:14:06,270
快去，你得吃点什么
Come on, get somethin' to eat.

1680
01:14:06,300 --> 01:14:08,040
在这里烦恼加布的事也没帮助
Ain't no sense in you fretting over Gabe.

1681
01:14:08,110 --> 01:14:09,210
罗斯，我有点事要跟你说
Rose, I got something to tell you.

1682
01:14:09,240 --> 01:14:12,210
- 待我把食物放好再说  - 罗斯…
- Wait till I put the food on the table.  - Rose...

1683
01:14:13,040 --> 01:14:16,010
我不知道该怎开口
Now, I don't know how to tell you this.

1684
01:14:19,850 --> 01:14:21,950
但又不能瞒着你
And I can't explain it none.

1685
01:14:21,950 --> 01:14:25,120
[好感]就那么一点点的积聚啊
It just sort of grows on you.

1686
01:14:26,060 --> 01:14:29,190
开始时就像小木灌
It started off like a little bush,

1687
01:14:29,190 --> 01:14:30,830
待你发现时已经是整片森林了
next thing you know, it's a whole forest.

1688
01:14:30,830 --> 01:14:32,060
特洛伊，你在说什么？
Troy, what is you talking about?

1689
01:14:32,060 --> 01:14:33,960
我在说话，女人，让我把话说完
I'm talking, woman. Let me talk.

1690
01:14:33,960 --> 01:14:35,930
我在跟你说
I'm trying to tell you,

1691
01:14:35,930 --> 01:14:38,230
我在找个隐晦的方法跟你说…
find a way to tell you that...

1692
01:14:43,240 --> 01:14:45,870
我要成为父亲了
I'm gonna be a daddy.

1693
01:14:47,940 --> 01:14:50,150
对，我要成为别人的父亲了
Yeah, I'm gonna be somebody's daddy.

1694
01:14:54,850 --> 01:14:57,520
特洛伊，不是真的吧？你要成为什么？
Troy, you ain't telling me this. You're gonna be what?

1695
01:14:57,520 --> 01:14:58,990
- 你要成为别人的父亲？ - 罗斯…
- You're gonna be somebody's daddy?  - Rose...

1696
01:14:58,990 --> 01:15:00,090
你竟然跟你的妻子说这个？
You're telling your wife this?

1697
01:15:00,090 --> 01:15:01,160
现在…
Now...

1698
01:15:01,160 --> 01:15:03,530
嗨，特洛伊，嗨，罗斯
Hey, Troy! Hey, Rose!

1699
01:15:03,530 --> 01:15:06,160
我等了十八年就为了听你说这些事吗？
I got to wait 18 years to hear something like this?

1700
01:15:06,160 --> 01:15:07,800
嗨，罗斯
Hey, Rose.

1701
01:15:09,270 --> 01:15:11,930
我有朵花送给你
I got a flower for you.

1702
01:15:14,270 --> 01:15:18,070
那是朵玫瑰花，就像你的名字一样
That's a rose. The same rose like you is.

1703
01:15:23,010 --> 01:15:24,310
谢了，加布
Thanks, Gabe.

1704
01:15:24,310 --> 01:15:25,980
特洛伊，你没在生我的气吧？
Troy, you ain't mad at me?

1705
01:15:25,990 --> 01:15:28,010
那些坏人抓了我回来
Them bad mens come and put me away.

1706
01:15:28,020 --> 01:15:30,020
- 你没在生我的气吧？ - 没，我没有生气
- You ain't mad at me?  - No. No, I ain't mad at you.

1707
01:15:30,020 --> 01:15:32,020
十八年了，你竟然做得出这种事？
Eighteen years, and you want to come with this?

1708
01:15:32,020 --> 01:15:34,860
看我拿到了什么？一个全新的二十五美分
See what I got? Got a brand-new quarter.

1709
01:15:37,560 --> 01:15:38,760
罗斯，只是…
Rose, it's just that...

1710
01:15:39,260 --> 01:15:41,030
你没什么可以说，也不用解释
Ain't nothing you can say, Troy. Ain't no explaining it.

1711
01:15:41,030 --> 01:15:43,900
给我这二十五美分的人还有一大堆
The fella that give me this quarter had a whole mess of 'em!

1712
01:15:43,900 --> 01:15:46,230
我要留着它直到它暗哑无光
I'm gonna keep this quarter till it stops shining.

1713
01:15:46,240 --> 01:15:49,040
加布，出去前门等我，我冰箱里有西瓜
Gabe, go on up front now. I got some watermelon in the frigidaire.

1714
01:15:49,110 --> 01:15:50,210
快去，我待会拿给你
Go on. I'll get you a piece.

1715
01:15:50,240 --> 01:15:53,040
罗斯，听我说，我当时在追赶地狱之犬
Say, Rose, you know, I was chasing hellhounds,

1716
01:15:53,040 --> 01:15:56,040
然后那些坏人把我抓回去锁起来了
and them bad mens come and get me and take me away.

1717
01:15:56,050 --> 01:15:58,110
特洛伊救了我，他来了并跟他们说
Troy helped me. He come down there and told them

1718
01:15:58,110 --> 01:16:01,120
他们最好在他打跨他们之前放了我
they better let me go before he beat them up!

1719
01:16:01,190 --> 01:16:02,290
他真的说了
Yeah, he did!

1720
01:16:02,320 --> 01:16:04,920
出去吧，加布，我待会给你西瓜
Go up front now, Gabe. I'll get you some watermelon.

1721
01:16:04,920 --> 01:16:06,250
那些坏人都走了
Them bad men is gone now.

1722
01:16:06,260 --> 01:16:08,920
好吧，罗斯要给我西瓜
Okay. Rose gonna give me some watermelon,

1723
01:16:08,930 --> 01:16:11,290
有条纹的那种
the kind with the stripes on it.

1724
01:16:16,930 --> 01:16:18,230
为什么，特洛伊？
Why, Troy?

1725
01:16:20,030 --> 01:16:21,040
为什么？
Why?

1726
01:16:21,040 --> 01:16:26,940
过了那么多年，你现在跟我说这些？
After all these years, you come dragging this in to me now?

1727
01:16:26,940 --> 01:16:29,110
你这年纪，不应该会做的
It don't make no sense at your age.

1728
01:16:29,610 --> 01:16:33,650
我可以理解你十年或者十五年前这样做，但不是现在
I could've expected this 10, or 15 years ago, but not now.

1729
01:16:33,650 --> 01:16:36,120
年龄与此没有关系，罗斯
Age ain't got nothing to do with it, Rose.

1730
01:16:40,090 --> 01:16:43,320
我做了一个妻子该做的
I done tried to be everything a wife should be.

1731
01:16:45,260 --> 01:16:46,930
一个妻子可以做的所有事
Everything a wife could be.

1732
01:16:46,960 --> 01:16:48,130
我结婚整整十八年了
I've been married 18 years,

1733
01:16:48,460 --> 01:16:50,630
而现在竟到了你说
and now, I got to live to see the day you tell me

1734
01:16:50,630 --> 01:16:54,240
你和别的女人有了孩子的一天
you been seeing another woman and done fathered a child by her.

1735
01:17:07,280 --> 01:17:11,350
你明知道我不喜欢同父异母什么的
And you know I never wanted no half-nothing in my family!

1736
01:17:14,290 --> 01:17:15,660
我整个家庭都是这样
My whole family is half.

1737
01:17:15,660 --> 01:17:17,430
每个人都有不同的父母亲
Everybody got different fathers and mothers

1738
01:17:17,430 --> 01:17:19,190
我的几个兄弟姊妹都是这样
and my two sisters and my brothers.

1739
01:17:19,200 --> 01:17:21,000
你根本不知道谁是谁生的
You could hardly tell who's who.

1740
01:17:21,000 --> 01:17:22,660
永远不能好好谈谈父母的话题
Could never sit down and talk about papa and mama.

1741
01:17:22,670 --> 01:17:25,330
因为大家的父母都不一样
It was always your papa, your mama, my papa, my mama.

1742
01:17:25,340 --> 01:17:28,100
我从不想我的孩子们也是这样
And I ain't never wanted that for none of my children!

1743
01:17:28,100 --> 01:17:29,340
然而现在，你竟然过来
And now, you want to drag your behind in here

1744
01:17:29,410 --> 01:17:30,510
跟我说这些事！
and tell me something like this!

1745
01:17:30,540 --> 01:17:33,470
够了，你有权利知道的，是时候了
Stop it now. You ought to know. It's time for you to know.

1746
01:17:33,480 --> 01:17:34,380
我才不想知道，妈的！
Well, I don't want to know, god damn it!

1747
01:17:54,300 --> 01:17:55,300
罗斯
Rose?

1748
01:17:58,430 --> 01:18:02,100
我不能让她堕胎，米已成炊了
I just can't make it go away. It's done now.

1749
01:18:02,110 --> 01:18:06,170
我没法改变事情
I can't wish the circumstances of the thing away.

1750
01:18:06,180 --> 01:18:08,740
你也不想改变
And you don't want to, either.

1751
01:18:08,750 --> 01:18:10,510
或许你想我们两母子离开
Maybe you want to wish me and my boy away.

1752
01:18:10,510 --> 01:18:12,180
也许那就是你想的
Maybe that's what you want.

1753
01:18:12,180 --> 01:18:14,720
你不能这样做
Well, you can't wish us away.

1754
01:18:14,720 --> 01:18:16,750
我把我的十八年放在你身上了
I got 18 years of my life invested in you.

1755
01:18:16,750 --> 01:18:19,020
你该留在我们的床上而不是出去鬼混
You ought to have stayed upstairs in my bed where you belong.

1756
01:18:19,020 --> 01:18:21,460
听着，我们可以处理好这事
Now, listen to me. We can get a handle on this thing.

1757
01:18:21,460 --> 01:18:23,590
我们可以说清楚，有共识
We can talk this out, come to an understanding.

1758
01:18:23,590 --> 01:18:24,760
突然间此事就是关于“我们”
All of a sudden it's "we."

1759
01:18:24,760 --> 01:18:26,190
当你在外面
Where was "we" at when you were down there,

1760
01:18:26,200 --> 01:18:27,760
跟那个可恶的女人鬼混时“我们”在哪里？
rolling around with some godforsaken woman?

1761
01:18:27,760 --> 01:18:29,000
“我们”该在你做傻事之前
"We" should've come to an understanding

1762
01:18:29,000 --> 01:18:30,430
就要有共识！
before you started making a damn fool of yourself!

1763
01:18:30,430 --> 01:18:32,100
当说到共识时
You're a day late and a dollar short

1764
01:18:32,100 --> 01:18:33,400
你总是迟了
when it comes to an understanding with me.

1765
01:18:33,400 --> 01:18:39,310
罗斯，只是因为她能给我完全不同的感觉
Rose, it's just that she...gives me a different idea.

1766
01:18:39,740 --> 01:18:43,080
完全不同的自我理解
A different understanding about myself.

1767
01:18:43,080 --> 01:18:46,450
让我可以在这里走出去时，放下所有压力
I can step out of this house and get away from the pressures

1768
01:18:46,450 --> 01:18:48,080
和问题，变成一个完全不同的人
and the problems, be a different man.

1769
01:18:48,080 --> 01:18:50,020
我不用担心如何修好屋顶
I ain't got to worry about how I'll get the roof fixed,

1770
01:18:50,020 --> 01:18:51,490
或者付钱，或者…
or pay the bills, or...

1771
01:18:51,490 --> 01:18:53,120
我可以
I can just

1772
01:18:55,020 --> 01:18:57,460
成为一个我前所未有过的自己
be a part of myself I ain't never been before.

1773
01:18:58,530 --> 01:19:01,060
我想知道的是…
What I want to know is...

1774
01:19:03,330 --> 01:19:06,070
我想知道的是
What I want to know

1775
01:19:06,070 --> 01:19:08,540
你是否打算继续见她？
is do you plan to continue seeing her?

1776
01:19:08,540 --> 01:19:11,170
那就是你可以说的
That's all you can say to me.

1777
01:19:12,270 --> 01:19:14,110
我在她的家里能放松下来
I could sit up in her house and laugh.

1778
01:19:14,110 --> 01:19:16,380
你明白吗？
You understand what I'm saying?

1779
01:19:16,380 --> 01:19:19,180
我可以放声笑，而那感觉真好
I could laugh out loud, and it feels good.

1780
01:19:19,180 --> 01:19:21,380
简直好到了我心底里
It reaches all the way down to the bottom of my shoes.

1781
01:19:21,380 --> 01:19:22,580
罗斯，我…
Rose, I...

1782
01:19:25,120 --> 01:19:28,090
我不想放弃那些
I can't give that up.

1783
01:19:33,530 --> 01:19:35,830
那或许你该继续留在她那里
Well, maybe you ought to go on and stay down there with her,

1784
01:19:35,830 --> 01:19:37,530
如果她真是比我更好的女人的话
if she's a better woman than me.

1785
01:19:37,530 --> 01:19:39,400
这不是关于谁是更好的女人的问题
It ain't about nobody being a better woman, or nothing.

1786
01:19:39,470 --> 01:19:40,470
罗斯，你尽责了
Rose, you ain't to blame.

1787
01:19:40,500 --> 01:19:43,270
做妻子的话你简直是不二之选
A man couldn't ask for a better wife than you've been.

1788
01:19:43,270 --> 01:19:44,780
这事我得负起所有责任
I'm responsible for it.

1789
01:19:44,780 --> 01:19:46,810
我每天重复做着同样的事
I done locked myself into a pattern,

1790
01:19:46,810 --> 01:19:48,480
照顾你们，都让我忘了自己了
trying to take care of you all, that I forgot about myself.

1791
01:19:48,480 --> 01:19:50,280
我不是一直在你背后吗？
Well, what the hell was I there for?

1792
01:19:50,280 --> 01:19:51,850
那是我的工作，不是他人的
That was my job, not somebody else's.

1793
01:19:51,850 --> 01:19:55,150
罗斯，听着，我竭尽所能去过正当的生活
Rose, listen to me. I done tried all my life to live decent.

1794
01:19:55,150 --> 01:19:58,150
一个正当，努力向上的生活
To live a clean, hard, useful life.

1795
01:19:58,150 --> 01:20:01,320
我尽了力去成为一个好丈夫
I try to be a good husband to you, in every way I know how.

1796
01:20:01,320 --> 01:20:03,490
可能我一开始就错了吧，我不知道
Maybe I come into the world backwards, I don't know,

1797
01:20:03,490 --> 01:20:07,130
但你就像上场前已经被二振了一样
but you're born with two strikes on you before you come to the plate.

1798
01:20:07,200 --> 01:20:08,200
你得把任何事都看管好
You got to guard it closely,

1799
01:20:08,230 --> 01:20:10,870
老是担心突发事情
always looking for the curveball on the inside corner.

1800
01:20:10,870 --> 01:20:12,530
你不能让任何事不受你控制
You can't afford a called strike.

1801
01:20:12,540 --> 01:20:14,170
你不能让任何事漏掉
You can't let nothing get past you.

1802
01:20:14,170 --> 01:20:16,300
要是你倒下了，你还不死心
If you're going down, you're doing down swinging.

1803
01:20:16,310 --> 01:20:19,210
所有事都像对着你干一样
Everything lined up against you!

1804
01:20:20,580 --> 01:20:22,310
你还想怎样？
What you gonna do?

1805
01:20:23,650 --> 01:20:26,350
我赢了他们，罗斯，我短打了[牺牲]
I fooled them, Rose. I bunted.

1806
01:20:26,580 --> 01:20:30,520
当我有你和科丽和份有点像样的工作，我很安全
When I found you and Cory and a halfway decent job, I was safe.

1807
01:20:30,520 --> 01:20:32,850
没什么可以拖累我了
Couldn't nothing touch me!

1808
01:20:32,860 --> 01:20:34,420
我不会再被三振出局
I wasn't gonna strike out no more.

1809
01:20:34,420 --> 01:20:35,860
不会再回去坐牢
I wasn't going back to the penitentiary.

1810
01:20:35,860 --> 01:20:38,330
不会再喝醉，睡在街上
I wasn't gonna lie in the street with a bottle of wine.

1811
01:20:38,330 --> 01:20:42,600
我安全了，我有个家庭，有份工作
I was safe. I had me a family, a job.

1812
01:20:43,630 --> 01:20:46,500
我不会被三振的
I wasn't gonna get that last strike.

1813
01:20:48,340 --> 01:20:51,270
我站在一垒
I was standing on first base,

1814
01:20:51,270 --> 01:20:54,310
等着回到本垒
waiting for one of them boys to knock me in, to bring me home.

1815
01:20:54,310 --> 01:20:55,180
你该留在我们的床上，特洛伊
You should have stayed in my bed, Troy.

1816
01:20:55,180 --> 01:20:57,210
然后我看到那女子，她让我胆大起来
Then I saw the gal, she firmed up my backbone.

1817
01:20:57,210 --> 01:20:59,580
我在想如果我努力点，或许可以盗垒
I got to thinkin' that if I tried, maybe I could steal second.

1818
01:20:59,580 --> 01:21:01,380
- 你明白吗？ - 你该抱紧我
- You understand what I'm saying?  - You should've held me tight.

1819
01:21:01,380 --> 01:21:03,680
你该捉紧我的手
You should've grabbed me and held on.

1820
01:21:03,690 --> 01:21:04,620
我站在一垒十八年了
I stood on first base for 18 years,

1821
01:21:04,620 --> 01:21:07,260
然后我想，管他的，豁出去
and I thought, well, god damn it, go on for it!

1822
01:21:07,260 --> 01:21:09,590
我们不是在说棒球啊！
We ain't talking about baseball!

1823
01:21:09,590 --> 01:21:12,190
我们在说你跟别的女人鬼混
We talking about you going off and laying up with another woman,

1824
01:21:12,200 --> 01:21:13,230
然后把这事带回家跟我说
then bringing it home to me.

1825
01:21:13,230 --> 01:21:14,360
那才是我们要讨论的
That's what we're talking about.

1826
01:21:14,360 --> 01:21:17,470
- 我们不是要谈棒球！ - 罗斯，你没细心听
- We're not talkin' about no baseball!  - Rose, you're not listening to me.

1827
01:21:17,500 --> 01:21:19,630
我在用我最擅长的东西去表达
I'm trying to explain it to you the best way I know how.

1828
01:21:21,300 --> 01:21:22,800
对我来说很难去接受
It's not easy for me to admit

1829
01:21:22,800 --> 01:21:25,670
我站在原地十八年了这事实
that I've been standing in the same place for 18 years!

1830
01:21:25,680 --> 01:21:28,410
我也跟你一起站在原地啊！
Well, I've been standing with you!

1831
01:21:28,410 --> 01:21:32,480
我一直都跟你站在原地，特洛伊！我也有我的人生
I've been right here with you, Troy! I got a life, too.

1832
01:21:32,480 --> 01:21:36,680
我为此付出了我的十八年啊
I gave 18 years of my life to stand in the same spot as you!

1833
01:21:36,690 --> 01:21:38,720
你没想过我也想要做其他事？
Don't you think I ever wanted other things?

1834
01:21:38,720 --> 01:21:41,220
没想过我也有我的梦想和愿望？
Don't you think I had dreams and hopes?

1835
01:21:41,220 --> 01:21:43,660
那我的生命呢？那我呢？
What about my life? What about me?

1836
01:21:43,660 --> 01:21:45,260
你以为我没有想过
Don't you think it ever crossed my mind

1837
01:21:45,260 --> 01:21:46,430
去认识其他男人？
to want to know other men?

1838
01:21:46,430 --> 01:21:49,200
或者一走了之
That I wanted to lay up somewhere

1839
01:21:49,200 --> 01:21:50,700
忘了我的职责？
and forget about my responsibilities?

1840
01:21:50,700 --> 01:21:52,500
或者我想有过人让我笑
That I wanted someone to make me laugh,

1841
01:21:52,500 --> 01:21:54,570
让我快乐？
so I could feel good?

1842
01:21:54,570 --> 01:21:56,670
你不是唯一一个有需求的人
You're not the only one who's got wants and needs.

1843
01:21:56,670 --> 01:21:58,670
但我留下来了，特洛伊
But I held on to you, Troy.

1844
01:21:58,680 --> 01:22:03,210
我把我的所有情感，需求和梦想
I took all my feelings, my wants and needs and dreams,

1845
01:22:03,210 --> 01:22:04,950
埋藏在你的心底下
and I buried them inside you.

1846
01:22:04,950 --> 01:22:07,380
我把种子埋藏好，每天看着它，祈望它成长
I planted a seed and watched and prayed over it.

1847
01:22:07,380 --> 01:22:10,420
我把自己埋藏在你心内然后等待开花！
I planted myself inside you and waited to bloom!

1848
01:22:10,420 --> 01:22:12,290
但那花了我十八年时间
And it didn't take me no 18 years

1849
01:22:12,290 --> 01:22:14,390
才知道那泥土原来如石头般硬
to realize the soil was hard and rocky,

1850
01:22:14,390 --> 01:22:16,490
还有它根本不会开花！
and it wasn't never gonna bloom!

1851
01:22:16,490 --> 01:22:19,490
但我仍然捉紧你，我把你捉得更紧
But I held on to you, Troy. I held you tighter.

1852
01:22:19,500 --> 01:22:21,560
你是我的丈夫
You was my husband.

1853
01:22:21,560 --> 01:22:24,370
我该给你我的全部
I owed you everything I had.

1854
01:22:24,370 --> 01:22:27,240
我的每一部分
Every part of me I could find to give you.

1855
01:22:27,240 --> 01:22:30,970
当晚上我在楼上的睡房时
And upstairs in that bedroom, with the darkness falling in on me,

1856
01:22:30,970 --> 01:22:35,310
我用尽力气消除那个疑虑
I gave everything I had to try and erase the doubt

1857
01:22:35,310 --> 01:22:37,780
那个其实你不是个好男人的疑虑
that you wasn't the finest man in the world.

1858
01:22:37,780 --> 01:22:40,650
无论你打算去哪里，我都会跟着你
And wherever you was going, i was gonna be there with you,

1859
01:22:40,650 --> 01:22:43,380
因为你是我的丈夫
because you was my husband.

1860
01:22:44,590 --> 01:22:47,660
因为这样做我才能继续做你的妻子
'Cause that's the only way I was gonna survive as your wife.

1861
01:22:48,720 --> 01:22:51,330
你经常说给什么
You always talking about what you give

1862
01:22:51,330 --> 01:22:52,630
还有你不能给什么
and what you don't have to give.

1863
01:22:53,330 --> 01:22:55,000
但你也会拿取，特洛伊
But you take, too, Troy.

1864
01:22:55,000 --> 01:22:57,670
你会拿取而且不在乎是谁付出的
You take and don't even know nobody's giving.

1865
01:22:57,670 --> 01:22:59,730
你说我好逸恶劳
You say I take and don't give.

1866
01:22:59,810 --> 01:23:00,910
- 特洛伊，你弄痛我了  - 你说我好逸恶劳
- Troy, you're hurting me.  - You say I take and don't give.

1867
01:23:00,940 --> 01:23:02,400
- 特洛伊，我的手很痛，放手！ - 我给了我能给的
- Troy, you're hurting my arm, let go!  - I gave you everything I got.

1868
01:23:02,410 --> 01:23:03,470
别说我没有
Don't you tell that lie on me.

1869
01:23:03,470 --> 01:23:04,770
- 妈妈！ - 别说我没有
- Mama!  - Don't you tell that lie!

1870
01:23:04,770 --> 01:23:06,540
特洛伊，我弄痛我了！
Troy, you're hurting me!

1871
01:23:07,010 --> 01:23:08,510
特洛伊，特洛伊
Troy! Troy!

1872
01:23:08,710 --> 01:23:12,550
好了，那是二振
All right. That's strike two.

1873
01:23:13,380 --> 01:23:17,590
你别再惹我，你最好别三振
You stay away from around me, boy. Don't you strike out.

1874
01:23:19,320 --> 01:23:21,390
你满球数了
You're living with a full count.

1875
01:23:24,660 --> 01:23:26,630
你最好别三振！
Don't you strike out!

1876
01:26:46,930 --> 01:26:48,900
特洛伊，我想跟你说点事
Troy, I want to talk to you.

1877
01:26:51,600 --> 01:26:53,770
突然间？
All of a sudden?

1878
01:26:55,670 --> 01:26:58,040
过了这么久你想跟我说点事？
After all this time, you want to talk to me, huh?

1879
01:26:59,040 --> 01:27:00,740
你数个月来没跟我说过一句话
You ain't wanted to talk to me in months.

1880
01:27:00,740 --> 01:27:02,010
昨晚也没有
You ain't wanted to talk to me last night.

1881
01:27:02,010 --> 01:27:03,740
你那时可不想理会我
You didn't want no parts of me then.

1882
01:27:04,250 --> 01:27:06,510
现在你想来说什么？
What you want to talk to me about now?

1883
01:27:09,850 --> 01:27:11,590
明天是星期五
Tomorrow's Friday.

1884
01:27:11,590 --> 01:27:12,890
我知道
I know what day tomorrow is.

1885
01:27:12,890 --> 01:27:14,920
你以为我不知道吗？
You think I don't know tomorrow's Friday?

1886
01:27:14,920 --> 01:27:17,590
我的整生，都在等星期五的来临
My whole life, I ain't done nothing but look to see Friday coming,

1887
01:27:17,590 --> 01:27:18,260
你还来提醒我
and you got to tell me it's Friday.

1888
01:27:18,260 --> 01:27:19,590
我想知道你会否回家
I want to know if you're coming home.

1889
01:27:19,900 --> 01:27:22,600
我每天都回家，你知道的
I always come home, Rose. You know that.

1890
01:27:22,600 --> 01:27:23,860
没有一晚我是没回来的
Ain't never been a night I ain't come home.

1891
01:27:23,870 --> 01:27:25,800
你明知道那不是我的意思
That ain't what I mean, and you know it.

1892
01:27:25,800 --> 01:27:29,270
我想知道你下班后会否直接回家
I wanna know if you're coming straight home after work.

1893
01:27:29,270 --> 01:27:32,310
我想我会兑换支票，然后在泰勒的酒吧和他们喝点酒
I figured I'd cash my check, hang out at Taylors' with the boys.

1894
01:27:32,380 --> 01:27:33,580
或许玩一局[西洋]跳棋
Maybe play a game of checkers.

1895
01:27:33,610 --> 01:27:36,080
特洛伊，我不能再继续这样，我接受不了
Troy, I can't live like this. I won't live like this.

1896
01:27:36,080 --> 01:27:37,750
自那之后你就人在心不在
You're living on borrowed time with me.

1897
01:27:37,750 --> 01:27:39,780
六个月以来，你都没真正回来
Been going on six months now, you ain't been coming home.

1898
01:27:39,780 --> 01:27:41,880
我每晚都回来，一年来从没间断过
I come home every night. Every night of the year.

1899
01:27:41,880 --> 01:27:44,620
那就整整三百六十五天
That's 365 days.

1900
01:27:45,890 --> 01:27:48,690
我想你明天下班后直接回家
I want you to come home tomorrow after work.

1901
01:27:53,630 --> 01:27:57,100
罗斯，你知道我不会乱花钱
Rose, I don't mess up my pay. You know that.

1902
01:27:57,100 --> 01:27:59,070
我收到工资后就全数交给你
I take my pay, i give it to you.

1903
01:27:59,070 --> 01:28:02,740
我只拿着你分配给我的部份
I don't have no money but what you give me back.

1904
01:28:02,740 --> 01:28:05,910
我只想要一点私人时间而已
I just want a little time to myself.

1905
01:28:05,910 --> 01:28:07,070
去享乐一下
A little time to enjoy life.

1906
01:28:07,080 --> 01:28:09,040
那我呢？何时才轮到我去享乐？
What about me? When's my time to enjoy life?

1907
01:28:09,050 --> 01:28:11,310
我不知道还可以说什么，我已经尽力了
I don't know what to tell you, Rose. I'm doing the best I can.

1908
01:28:11,380 --> 01:28:12,680
你下班回家后
You ain't been comin' home from work,

1909
01:28:12,710 --> 01:28:13,880
只换件衣服又出去了
but time enough to change your clothes and run out.

1910
01:28:14,040 --> 01:28:15,950
你叫那尽力吗？
You wanna call that the best you can do?

1911
01:28:17,590 --> 01:28:20,720
我晚点得去医院看艾伯塔
I'm going over to the hospital to see Alberta.

1912
01:28:21,690 --> 01:28:23,360
她今天下午进了医院
She went into the hospital this afternoon.

1913
01:28:23,360 --> 01:28:26,890
看来是早产
Looks like she might have the baby early.

1914
01:28:27,760 --> 01:28:29,600
我不会去太久
I won't be gone long.

1915
01:28:35,800 --> 01:28:37,710
你该知道他们今天到了珀尔小姐那里
Well, you ought to know. They went over to Miss Pearl's

1916
01:28:37,780 --> 01:28:38,880
带走了加布
and got Gabe today.

1917
01:28:38,910 --> 01:28:42,810
她说你叫他们锁起他来
She said you told them to go ahead and lock him up.

1918
01:28:42,810 --> 01:28:46,850
我才没有说过，你被她骗了
I ain't said no such thing. Whoever told you that is telling a lie.

1919
01:28:46,850 --> 01:28:48,720
珀尔小姐撒了个很大的谎
Miss Pearl ain't doing nothing but telling a big, fat lie.

1920
01:28:48,720 --> 01:28:50,680
她不用说出口，我在文件上看到的
She ain't had to tell me. I read it on the papers.

1921
01:28:50,690 --> 01:28:52,820
- 那份文件说了什么？ - 说你叫他们去带走他
- What'd it say, huh?  - It said you told them to take him.

1922
01:28:52,820 --> 01:28:54,340
那他们肯定弄错了
Oh, well, then they screwed that up,

1923
01:28:54,370 --> 01:28:55,860
就像他们弄错其他事一样
just like they screw up everything.

1924
01:28:55,890 --> 01:28:56,920
我才不在意他们在文件上说了什么
I ain't worried about what they got on that paper.

1925
01:28:56,920 --> 01:28:58,390
说政府会把他的部分财产交给医院作照顾费用
It say the government sends part of the check to the hospital,

1926
01:28:58,460 --> 01:28:59,560
另一部份交给你
the other part to you.

1927
01:28:59,590 --> 01:29:02,130
我跟此事毫无关系
I ain't got nothing to do with that, if that's the way it works.

1928
01:29:02,130 --> 01:29:02,630
我也没叫他们分给我
I don't make up the rules...

1929
01:29:02,630 --> 01:29:03,830
你对待加布就像你对待科丽一样差劲
You did Gabe just like you did Cory.

1930
01:29:03,830 --> 01:29:05,030
你不会替科丽签署
You wouldn't sign the paper for Cory,

1931
01:29:05,030 --> 01:29:06,830
但你却替加布签了，是你签的！
but you signed for Gabe! You signed that paper!

1932
01:29:06,840 --> 01:29:09,800
我说过我没有签署过什么，女人
I told you I ain't signed nothing, woman.

1933
01:29:09,800 --> 01:29:11,370
天啊，我只签了份释放同意书
Hell, the only thing I signed was the release form.

1934
01:29:11,440 --> 01:29:11,840
我又不识字
Hell, I can't read,

1935
01:29:11,870 --> 01:29:12,910
天知道他们在同意书上写了什么
I don't know what they had on that paper.

1936
01:29:12,910 --> 01:29:14,840
我才没签过什么送走加布的文件
I ain't signed nothing about sending Gabe away.

1937
01:29:14,840 --> 01:29:17,040
我当时说送他到医院，你说要让他自由
I said send him to the hospital, you said let him go free.

1938
01:29:17,120 --> 01:29:18,220
现在你反过来
Then you went down there

1939
01:29:18,250 --> 01:29:20,380
同意送他到医院，就为了他的钱
and you signed him to the hospital for half his money.

1940
01:29:20,380 --> 01:29:20,950
这是自相矛盾，特洛伊
You went back on yourself, Troy.

1941
01:29:20,950 --> 01:29:22,980
你会有报应的
You're gonna have to answer for that.

1942
01:29:22,980 --> 01:29:23,820
你才跟珀尔小姐说过话
You just been over there talking to Miss Pearl.

1943
01:29:23,820 --> 01:29:25,120
她只是因为不能再
She just mad 'cause she ain't gettin'

1944
01:29:25,120 --> 01:29:26,390
骗加布的钱而生气，所以胡说而已
Gabe's rent money, that's all it is.

1945
01:29:26,390 --> 01:29:28,320
特洛伊，我亲眼看着你签的！
Troy, I seen where you signed the paper!

1946
01:29:28,390 --> 01:29:29,090
你才没有！
You ain't seen nothing I signed!

1947
01:29:29,120 --> 01:29:31,930
那她家里为何又有我弟弟的文件？
And what she doing got papers on my brother for, anyway?

1948
01:29:32,060 --> 01:29:35,730
珀尔小姐只是在撒谎
Miss Pearl ain't doing nothing but telling a big, fat lie,

1949
01:29:35,730 --> 01:29:37,700
我会去跟她对质！
and I'm gonna tell her about it, too!

1950
01:29:43,410 --> 01:29:46,010
我没有签署过什么！
You ain't seen nothing I signed!

1951
01:29:46,740 --> 01:29:48,080
还说我…
Say...

1952
01:29:49,910 --> 01:29:52,080
我没有签署过什么！
You ain't seen nothing I signed!

1953
01:31:48,900 --> 01:31:50,260
特洛伊
Troy.

1954
01:31:52,530 --> 01:31:54,130
特洛伊
Troy.

1955
01:31:59,240 --> 01:32:02,210
那是医院打来说艾伯塔生下来了
That was the hospital. Alberta had the baby.

1956
01:32:03,550 --> 01:32:06,210
是吗？是男还是女的？
Yeah? What she have? What is it?

1957
01:32:07,180 --> 01:32:08,950
是个女孩
It's a girl.

1958
01:32:11,550 --> 01:32:13,190
我…
I...

1959
01:32:16,160 --> 01:32:18,360
我该去看她一下
I better get on down there to see her.

1960
01:32:20,200 --> 01:32:24,260
- 特洛伊  - 我总得去看她一下吧，罗斯
- Troy.  - I got to go see her now, Rose. That's only right.

1961
01:32:29,370 --> 01:32:33,010
怎么了？婴儿什么有问题吗？
What's the matter? Baby all right, ain't it?

1962
01:32:36,110 --> 01:32:39,210
艾伯塔产后死去了
Alberta died having the baby.

1963
01:32:40,280 --> 01:32:42,350
你说她死了？
She died? You say she's dead?

1964
01:32:45,390 --> 01:32:47,020
她死了？
Alberta dead?

1965
01:32:47,590 --> 01:32:50,120
他们说尽了力，他们…
They said they done all they could. They...

1966
01:32:51,360 --> 01:32:53,060
他们对她无能为力
They couldn't do nothing for her.

1967
01:33:24,090 --> 01:33:27,060
那婴儿呢？她还好吗？
Oh, what about the baby? Baby all right?

1968
01:33:28,960 --> 01:33:31,060
他们说她很健康
They say it's healthy.

1969
01:33:33,200 --> 01:33:34,900
我在想谁会替她办身后事
I wonder who's gonna bury her.

1970
01:33:34,970 --> 01:33:36,070
她有家人的，罗斯
She had a family, Rose.

1971
